Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Rarity! Just the\Npony I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come to Twilight's class\Nwith me? It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd love to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to meet Rainbow Dash\Nfor our day of fun together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight wants to use you as\Nan example for the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your example is here!\NHa ha! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the example.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You both are. Because together,\Nyou perfectly demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,my lesson on compromise\Nin friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash and Rarity have\Nvery different interests
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that keep them busy. But being\Nfriends is so important to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they always manage to\Nmake time for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Day of Fun was hard to plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what with Rainbow Dash's\Nextremely time-consuming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and erratically scheduled\NWonderbolts practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rarity's{\i1} weird{\i0}\Nfashion seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's working on her\Nwinter collection
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not even summer yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still found\Ntime to be together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See, class? These\Nponies are models
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of true friendship in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for stopping by!\NEnjoy your "Day of Fun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, ooh! What amazing stuff\Nare you gonna do together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoe shopping!\NObstacle races!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dress shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight goggle shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come ON! I even said\N{\i1} shopping{\i0} that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect! We'll go\Nshopping first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I brought\Nstuff for Buckball-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we supposed to be\Nlearning something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause this doesn't sound\Nlike compromising at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You guys have nothing in\Ncommon. How can you be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Rainbow\NDash and Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoy doing different things,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there are plenty of reasons\Nwhy they're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. We've {\i1}always{\i0} been friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no. Not{\i1} always.{\i0} But\Nfor like a super long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know all\Nthe same ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was that time during the\NCloudsdale Best Young Flyer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,competition when I totally saved\NRarity's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And {\i1}I{\i0} once proved\NRainbow Dash's innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to her beloved Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,when she was being framed\Nfor a mysterious incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, look, it may seem like\NRarity and Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have that\Nmuch in common
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when you try to put\Nit into words..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes friendships\Ncan't be explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to see them\Nin action to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... that's\Na great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go about your Day of\NFun as you normally would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't even know we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Game On!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! You were supposed\Nto be holding your bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Oh, sorry, darling! Wearing\Nthis drab jersey gave me an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for a Buckball-inspired\Nline of "athleisure wear"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that would allow for maximum\Nflexibility and style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm ready now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Cause this time I'm\Ngonna try something new
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and super-intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Are you even\Npaying attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, I mean, of course! I\Nheld my bucket and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to\NCATCH the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, that\Nsounds dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, forget it. She's\Nnever gonna understand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the point of this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Buckball time is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. see? They did something\NRainbow Dash likes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so now it's time for something\NRarity likes. Compromise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. I'm genuinely not\Nsure. Are they too in style?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, isn't that what\Nyou want them to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. But they should\Nbe ahead of the curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're in\Nfashion right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then they're\Npractically already out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Perhaps I should get\Nthe stilettos instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you like tripping\Nwith every step,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,heels on a horse\Nare pretty useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[snort]{\i1} Au contraire!{\i0} They're perfect\Nin a multitude of situations:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Formal functions, afternoon\Nteas, evening teas, high teas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,tea by the sea, royal tea--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can they clean up glitter?\NEw! It's on my hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}so{\i0} boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash and\NRarity are just... er..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,showcasing an aspect of\Nfriendship called "banter":
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the playful and friendly\Nexchange of remarks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in good fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh I cannot wait! Collecting\Ngemstones is my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, something we can\Nagree on: treasure hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See, everycreature?\NThat didn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're having a\Ngreat time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh{\i1} Magnifique!{\i0} This will\Nbe perfect for the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,emerald-encrusted romper\NI've been working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! Now what would\Nbe even cooler
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is if we could find a treasure\Nchamber or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if I were a secret\Ndoor, where would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Could you please\Nrefrain from all of that racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's muddying my\Nconcentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Look! A lever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stuck. Come\Nhelp me, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] You{\i1} ruined{\i0} my gems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well. {\i1}You{\i0} ruined\Nmy treasure hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. This wasn't about treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about finding gemstones\Nfor my winter collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about clothes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be on\Nan adventure together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That. Is. It! This "Day of\NFun" is officially OVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by ME! Maybe I can spend\Nsome time doing something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually like now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. heh heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you don't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just having\Na little.. disagreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes that happens between\Npals. But no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,they can always get past the\Nproblem and stay good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care about any\Nof the things I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always about you\Nand your boring fashions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Please!{\i1} You{\i0} don't even\Ngive my interests a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have absolutely no\Nrespect for the finer things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,NO RESPECT, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[both]\NI guess we're just\NNOT FRIENDS ANYMORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there was the\Ntime Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,called my Cloudsdale\NCouture Boutique idea
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"impractical"! Imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I'd\Nneeded Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to perform the Butterfly\NWing spell on me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever I wanted to\Ndeliver merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told her a thousand\Ntimes Pegasi don't even want
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,restrictive, heavy dresses! We\Nneed to be able to fly. Duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the day I was\Nwearing a{\i1} really{\i0} gorgeous hat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rainbow Dash\Ndidn't even notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts\Nshow was RUINED!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity's hat was blocking\Neverypony's view!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,ENOUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Guidance counseling is for\Ntalking out your problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,not telling me everything\Nthat's ever happened
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the history of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've learned sometimes\Ntalking isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to put yourselves\Nin one another's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way am I wearing those.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[groan]\NWhat I'm saying is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we need a way to help you\Ntwo reconnect. Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The library? And\Nthis helps us how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You both love books!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash never\Nstops talking about\NDaring Do adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a huge fan of\NShadow Spade mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfect way for you\Ntwo to reconnect as friends
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is to read each\Nother's favorite book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll read them, too! Then\Nwe'll all discuss afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a "Good\NFriends Book Club"! OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring snacks..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! We're all here! To\Nstart, why don't you two
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,share one thing you liked\Nabout each other's books?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, I'll go first! Erm.. I\Nreally enjoyed the part in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Daring Do and the\NRazor of Dreams"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when Daring used a vicious\NCragadile as a raft and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh sorry, it's just that I\Nfind those action sequences
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so ridiculously\Nover-the-top.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're real.. you've\Neven met Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but the book's\Ndescriptions just drag on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about all those\Nsilly, unpronounceable names?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor whozit, whatsit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cab-a-YAIR-on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,CAB-A-LER-ON! Just like it\Nlooks! How hard is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh tea, anypony?\NCucumber sandwich? Heh..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we could go over some nice,\Nfriendly talking points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! Seriously? Don't\Neven get me started
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,on those clothing\Ndescriptions in Shadow Spade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What a yawn fest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... the outfit\Ndescriptions are an integral part of the plot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of "The Colt in Crimson:\NA Shadow Spade Mystery"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you\Ndidn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that Sir Fluffingsworth\Nvon Radishfield
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,wears only silk,\Ndouble-breasted waistcoats,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd never deduce that\Nhe, in fact, was the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] You didn't\Neven read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see I'm gonna\Nneed reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my fault it's so\Nboring it put me to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't be bothered\Nto read the thing I like,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that just further\Nillustrates the point
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have nothing\Nin common anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we agree on\Nthat! From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only hanging out\Nwith ponies who "get" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your drama can wait!\NTwilight needs help, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's GONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Amulet of Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! One of the magical items\Nyou've been keeping
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for Princess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That amulet can reverse the\Ntides and summon tsunamis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If it falls into the\Nwrong hooves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria will be\Nin grave danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know tons about searching\Nfor lost treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I follow the\Nculprit's clues,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain I can find\Nwho took your amulet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! I'll\Nfeel so much better
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing you two are\Nlooking for it.. together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,While WE work on\Na locator spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There appear to be\Nno signs of damage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to the surrounding\Nartifacts,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,suggesting the thief\Ndid not leave in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,RARITY! Your boots are leaving\Nsparkles all over the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft. Those aren't from my\Nboots. Mine are magenta,\Nnot blue. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out these boots were\Nnot "made for trotting",
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as advertised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?\NWe promised Twilight we'd work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Amulet of Aurora is\Nmade out of Azurantium!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Azurantium? You know,\Nthe same metal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Amulet of Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from Daring Do Book\N4 is made from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It always leaves sparkles\Nwherever it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this. Remember? It's\Nfrom the book you JUST READ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[nervous chuckle]\NThat book yes. The one I - I just read. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? After giving\Nme all that grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't read\Nmine either!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrr. As soon as we find this\Namulet, we are DONE with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, slow down!\NYou're flying past important clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a print, but\Ndefinitely not a hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those claw marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? I found\Na bigger clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't\Nexpect me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[shudder] WADE through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's too deep.\NWe'll get stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh clever! What Daring Do book\Ndid you get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I learned it at\NScootaloo's Filly Guides camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ach. At least you can fly across...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! If one of those geysers\Nburns off my wingfeathers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be out of the\NWonderbolts for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I could try and\Nslingshot my way through,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd need two\Nperfectly placed trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,some stretchy rope,\Nand a pith helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad we can't\Ndo what Daring Do did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in book 4 and find a\NCragadile for a raft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta da! The SS Cragadile,\Nat your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. That. Is... Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean... it's all\Nright. I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nhow to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! We may have been friends\N"for a super long time",
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't know\NEVERYTHING about me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] The glitter trail! It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to find\Nthe Amulet of Aurora now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[very quietly] Ow, ears!\NWhy hoof-hoofs yell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Too-too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Too-too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a Bufogren! They\Nhave really sensitive ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[whispering] Did you happen to\Nsee anycreature
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with a sparkly\Nthingy go this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His breath smells so\Nbad I can't think!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't hear him\Nfrom back here. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! I think I have\Nthe perfect solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An old unicorn beauty trick.\NThat is, if you can somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,procure us a tiny\Nbit of cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that! I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! It's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[nasal] Uh. Excuse me, kind sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a special\Ntreat for you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in exchange\Nfor your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a magical\NUnicorn delicacy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,called "Effervescence".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Very now, very chic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Sorry. Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm. Mm.\NMuh mouth. Fresh and minty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Good! Now which way did\Nthe sparkly thing go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Up-up! Up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you\Nwaiting for? Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly up there and\Nget that amulet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. we're doing this\Ntogether, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can we? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I wasn't leaving\Nyou behind in that swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... maybe the key to\Nunlocking this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is in these inscriptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or.. perhaps the\Nkey is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't decide between\Nthe boots and the stilettos,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so I got both.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,High heels can\Ndo that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you called\Nthem useless..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said that. Or\Nmade fun of the other stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you like to do. Some of\Nit's actually sorta neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you an apology, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Buckball may not be my thing,\Nbut it's something you enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're very good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have\Ntreated your interests
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,like they were worth\Nless than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So... does this mean\Nwe're still friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would very\Nmuch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go find\Nthat amulet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. That tunnel\Nleads to the SCHOOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret passage!\NAWESOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Spikey-Wikey, you\Nstole the Amulet of Aurora!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... this was a\Nsetup to make us get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interfere,\Nbut you both--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reaaally needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So even though you don't like\Nany of the same stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you two are friends again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Always. I think we just\Nneeded a teensy reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We don't have to\Nlove the exact same things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to have fun together. I\Nmean, imagine if we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How boring would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When we give each other\Na chance to share the\Ndifferent things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we enjoy, it can be\Nsurprisingly wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Too bad we wasted\Nour Day of Fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a\Nlittle time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna... go hit the shops?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I could actually\Nuse your help
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,picking out some\Nnew Buckball gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,DO I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But... only if you help me choose\Nsome Buckball fan attire,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can cheer for\Nmy favorite player
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,at the drop of a fabulous hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, YEAH! Let's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Good friends always work\Nthrough their differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] Even if it takes\Na little help.
